LAB_1:Networking and interface configuration
Step-1
-First logged into pfsense web GUI
-next navigate to interfaces->Assignments
Step-2
-Go to interfaces->LAN
-Set ipv4 configuration to static ipv4
-Assigned to ip address 192.168.10.1/24
-save and apply changes
Step-3
-Next renamed interfaces to 
LAN->LANCORE
WAN->WANUPLINK
-save and aplply changes
Step-4
-Next Reboot pfsense
Diagnostics->Reboot
-after reboot it displayed GUI page
-verified interface names and ip configuration
Step-5
-change the MTU
-next navigated to interfaces->lancore
-set mtu value to 1500
-save and apply changes
-next verify mtu changes in the interface page
status->interfaces
Step-6
-next disable any one of the interface
-select any interface (lancore or wanuplink)
-in this disable the interface
-save and apply changes
Step-7
-verify the traffic
-status->interfaces
-traffic is blocked

